-- Schaeuble May Raise Tax on German Soldiers’ Pay, Bild Says
-- B y   B r i a n   P a r k i n
-- 2012-03-07T07:15:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-07/schaeuble-may-raise-tax-on-german-soldiers-pay-bild-says.html
German Finance Minister  Wolfgang Schaeuble  may raise taxes on soldiers’ pay, the  Bild Zeitung 
reported, citing a Finance Ministry document.  Current tax rules exempt the pay of armed-service
volunteers, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Brian Parkin in Berlin at 
 bparkin@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
